:#202020\">Upgrade your website today with Premium Addons and elevate your content presentation.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Level Up Your Website with Elementor Pinterest Feed Widget</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">With Premium Pinterest Feed for Elementor widget, you can effortlessly showcase your pins and boards directly on your website. Previewing your Pinterest content has never been easier. You can select between three different layouts and four neat skins. Not just that, you can use the advanced filtering options to get pins from specific board(s), exclude specific pins, etc. Upgrade your Elementor experience with the Elementor Pinterest Feed widget from Premium Addons today!</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">We are inviting you to go and see the live Pinterest Feed widget&#8217;s <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-pinterest-feed-widget\">demo</a> layouts.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-50 is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/premium-addons-for-elementor/\" style=\"border-radius:0px;background-color:#222c75\"><strong>Free Download</strong></a></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-50 is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/pro/\" style=\"border-radius:0px;background-color:#e88000\"><strong>Get PA PRO</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Elementor Smart Post Listing widget got improved</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">We&#8217;ve added a Load More Button option that uses AJAX to load more posts to make your page faster and prevent overloading your server on page load. We also added a new style for the widget title and fixed some issues related to the Filters Menu! </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Additionally, we fixed the issue that the Spanish language in our Elementor Weather Forecast widget.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Discover the enhanced browsing experience. Visit the widget <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-smart-post-listing-widget/\"><strong>demo</strong></a> page today!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"538\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxNjAwIDg0MCIgd2lkdGg9IjE2MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iODQwIiBkYXRhLXU9Imh0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGcHJlbWl1bWFkZG9ucy5jb20lMkZ3cC1jb250ZW50JTJGdXBsb2FkcyUyRjIwMjMlMkYwNyUyRnRlc3QuanBnIiBkYXRhLXc9IjE2MDAiIGRhdGEtaD0iODQwIiBkYXRhLWJpcD0iIj48L3N2Zz4=\" data-spai=\"1\" alt=\"Elementor Smart Post Listing Improvements\" class=\"wp-image-58553\" srcset=\" \" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Elementor Smart Post Listing Improvements</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Alternative Gold API option in Elementor News Ticker widget</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">We got messages from our users that the gold data is not showing anymore because the Gold API quota was exceeded. So, an alternative Gold API Key option in our News Ticker widget has been added! Now, you can add an alternative API to ensure uninterrupted gold price updates when the quota of the primary API is exceeded.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Uncover the latest features. Dive into our News Tickers widget <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-news-ticker-widget/\"><strong>demo</strong></a> page now!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video autoplay loop muted src=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/alternative-gold-api-option-added-to-news-ticker-widget.mp4\"></video><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Elementor News Ticker Widget Alternative Gold API</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">In conclusion, Premium Addons is thrilled to introduce the Elementor Pinterest Feed widget, designed exclusively for our valued users. Seamlessly preview pins, enhance user experience with Smart Post Listing, and keep your audience engaged with the News Ticker&#8217;s alternative API option. Elevate your content presentation and unleash the power of innovation.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-50 is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/premium-addons-for-elementor/\" style=\"border-radius:0px;background-color:#222c75\"><strong>Free Download</strong></a></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-50 is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/pro/\" style=\"border-radius:0px;background-color:#e88000\"><strong>Get PA PRO</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-he